name: Johnathan ROBINS, Petitioner v. PHILADELPHIA COUNTY CLERK OF COURTS ACCOUNTING UNIT, Respondent

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 8th day of March, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus and the Petition to Amend Mandamus are DENIED, and Respondent’s Preliminary Objection is DISMISSED AS MOOT.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
